org.openbel.framework.core.indexer
Class JDBMEquivalenceLookup

java.lang.Object
  org.openbel.framework.core.indexer.JDBMEquivalenceLookup
All Implemented Interfaces:
EquivalenceLookup
public final class JDBMEquivalenceLookup
extends Object
implements EquivalenceLookup

Provides lookups via JDBM within BEL Equivalence Files (.beleq).
This lookup contains namespace values as the key, UUID (as a SkinnyUUID) as the value.

Author:
Steve Ungerer
